{"tid":1893844,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"買唔到配件跪求分享豬咀秘技","createTime":"2020-02-23T13:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T15:49:04.000Z","uid":327169,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"10a8d7cf705e3368f45c575107c995ea198f8e97","tid":1893844,"uid":327169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T13:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係我呢個八婆仔，最近越黎越多手足用豬咀代替口罩，豬咀配件濾棉都搶得七七八八，買到蓋又買唔到個盒底咁點算?<br />\n<br />\n係呀，講緊3M 501+603+5n11囉! <br />\n<br />\n之前好多手足都用過6006+5n11+501呢個組合，而家支那肺炎其實夾埋個濾罐用係好嘥料，有N95級數嘅5n11已經足夠，但係臨時臨急又揾唔到603點呀??? <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />揾個用過用完嘅罐挖空佢咪得囉!<br />\n個罐裡面全部都係活性碳粒粒，再用過濾紙夾住嘅，只要用個尖咀鉗先篤穿個圓形底，漏咁啲活性碳粒出黎先，然後面嗰張過濾紙就好易篤甩佢㗎喇，最後用你自己嘅方法將嗰兩張過濾紙分屍拎出黎就大功告成!<br />\n<br />\n記住戴口罩戴手套先好整呀，用過有毒㗎! 當然要洗乾淨先用得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n得咗<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bbJR6qo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbbJR6qo.jpg&h=27da3cc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你哋仲有咪秘技分享呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a2c7cf6b482b8df4af49c8887782619da6d10f","tid":1893844,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T13:53:58.000Z","msg":"唔換罐唔得咩"},{"pid":"ec8df82ecfeb3a8658f6016793238857e994c428","tid":1893844,"uid":327169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87a2c7cf6b482b8df4af49c8887782619da6d10f","tid":1893844,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T13:53:58.000Z","msg":"唔換罐唔得咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T14:08:07.000Z","msg":"都得嘅，重啲囉，同埋個罐就算平時去街唔係濾毒氣都有壽命㗎"},{"pid":"b5ed2d7e53cd4c174026a9c189bccfe357d16297","tid":1893844,"uid":73979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"10a8d7cf705e3368f45c575107c995ea198f8e97","tid":1893844,"uid":327169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c